Researchinterest
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
ProfessorHanleadsaresearchgroupofover30researchersinthedepartmentofMaterialsScienceandEngineeringatZhejiangUniversity.Hismajorinterestcoversthenovelsynthesisstrategy,thestructuralstudy,thefunctionalmanipulationandtheapplicationinvestigationoftheinorganicfunctionalmaterials.Majorfacetsofinvestigationincludestheadvancedsilicon-basednano-compositefilm,II-VIcompoundsemiconductornano-composites,oxidematerialsnanofibreandnanotube,organic/inorganiccomposites,non-crystallinesiliconbasedstructuralfilm,energy-savingglassesandthenovelprocessingtechniques.Hehasactivelypursuedtheresearchinthefieldofinorganicnonmetallicmaterialsscienceandengineeringfor25years,publishingover400journalpapers.




